joke_list.joke: A blind man walks into a bar. And a table. And a chair.
What's orange and sounds like a parrot? A carrot.
What do you call a black guy flying a plane? A pilot, you f-----g racist.
The bartender says, "We don't serve time travelers here." A time traveler walks into a bar.
What do you call an alligator in a vest? An Investigator.
Schrodinger's cat walks into a bar. And doesn't.
I never make mistakes. I thought I did once; but I was wrong.
What did the fish say when he hit the wall? Dam.
Why are pirates called pirates? 'cause they arrr!
A dyslexic man walks in to a bra.
How many tickles does it take to get an octopus to laugh? Ten-tickles!
What is a fake spaghetti strand? An impasta!
How do you know if someone's a vegan? They'll tell you.
Plato and a Platypus walk into a bar. The bartender looks up and says: "What is this, a joke?"
